               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Ṣalota ʿǝṭan “Prayer of Incense” (fols. 5ra-63rb)
 - Prayer of
                     Incense for Sunday (ʿǝlätä ʾǝḥud) (fols. 47rb-63rb) 
 
 Additio
                     1.</summary>
